{{Weapon}}

== Overview ==
These [[:Category:Weapons (Mines)|mines]] are filled with the same volatile magma gas cocktail found in the powerful [[Morning Star]] weapon. Triggering one mine usually sets of a chain reaction.

== Where to Acquire ==
Magma Mines can be bought in the workshop after obtaining [[Magma Technology]].
